# FHI Fashionable Bundle

## Unleash your creativity and set new trends with a three-piece ensemble of color tools

Sku#: FHI-FASHIONABLE-BUNDLE

$ 1,021.50$ 913.00

Add To Cart

Calling all fashion designers! The FHI Fashionable Bundle is your opportunity to shine bright. We’ve combined three of our top tools — the Fashion, Home + Interiors Cotton Passport, the Metallic Shimmers Color Guide, and the Pantone Color Match Card — into a discounted bundle so you can make your next fashion statement anywhere, anytime.

The Cotton Passport is portable perfection. Whether you’re in the studio or on the go, you’ll always have our 2,800 trend right colors at your fingertips. It’s the fastest, easiest way to see and select Pantone FHI colors on cotton.

With 200 metallic and pearlescent shades, the Metallic Shimmers Color Guide adds some sparkle to your designs. Use it to ignite your inspiration, captivate the runway, and create collections that leave a lasting impression.

The Color Match Card makes it simple to translate real-world inspirations into their Pantone color equivalents — all you need to do is snap a photo with your phone! This tool is exclusive to the Pantone Connect platform, and with it, you can easily pull colors from Pantone’s color libraries to create and share digital palettes.

